## 7. Performance Expectations

### Response Time Comparison
| Component | Ollama (Local) | Groq (Cloud) |
|-----------|---|---|
| Network latency | ~0-5ms | ~100-300ms |
| Inference time | Variable (depends on GPU) | ~500-2000ms |
| Total E2E | 50-500ms | 600-2300ms |

**Note**: Groq may be faster despite network latency due to their optimized infrastructure.

### Throughput
- **Ollama**: Depends on local GPU
- **Groq**: Scales automatically, no local bottleneck

