## 10. Cost Impact Analysis

### Estimation (Monthly)
Assuming 1000 queries/day with average 500 input + 200 output tokens:

```
Daily tokens: 1000 × (500 + 200) = 700,000 tokens
Monthly tokens: 700,000 × 30 = 21,000,000 tokens
Estimated cost: 21M × $0.0005 / 1M = $10.50 / month

(Compare to: Local Ollama GPU infrastructure cost)
```

### Break-even Analysis
- If you own GPU infrastructure: Groq costs more (direct cost, but easier operations)
- If you rent GPU (cloud): Groq typically cheaper at scale
- Operational overhead: Groq significantly reduces (no local maintenance)

