## 11. Security Considerations

### API Key Management
- ✅ Store GROQ_API_KEY in .env (never commit to git)
- ✅ .gitignore should exclude .env file
- ✅ Rotate keys periodically
- ❌ Never log or print the full API key
- ✅ Use environment variables, not hardcoded strings

### Data Privacy
- Groq sees the prompts you send
- Consider: What sensitive data goes into queries?
- Review Groq's data retention policy in their docs

